big5%2Fnews%2F2017-11-09%2F60022525.html&d=e%2B11qaBe0KYJzSebqjOx1ROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6d6dcb71\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/news/2017-11-09/60022525.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中央社報道稱，董建華卸任特首後，並未離開政壇，而是穿梭於中美之間，推動兩國關系，而且角色重要，帶來不可估量的作用。<br />\n<br />\n 消息人士說，董建華所以能夠扮演這種角色，有多重因素，但最重要的是他既獲得美方信任，也可直接與北京領導人溝通。"},{"pid":"23fe46f8057a1bee01b63cf863e2bb332e0e1e2e","tid":463063,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"大紀元唔係話董建華係江派咩?<br />\n江派人馬竟然可以同Donald Trump握手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 睇黎江派又可以再戰50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0825e4f44224bf5a613e798e86d2e3345e4da405","tid":463063,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大紀元唔係話董建華係江派咩?<br />\n江派人馬竟然可以同Donald Trump握手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 睇黎江派又可以再戰50年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多維不是大紀元...  多維跟01係同一位老細"},{"pid":"4a334f286290bcd92c9056d8d51e3a90f62948b3","tid":463063,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}